videos.description: On one end of the court, Freddie Gillespie is able to force a turnover and keep the ball from flying out of bounds, which in turn sets up a near full-court heave and impressive bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's smooth ball movement shines in full-court sequence) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Baylor's smooth ball movement shines in full-court sequence

videos.description: Matthew Mayer drives into the paint and jumps up over his Kansas State defender for a 1st-half bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Baylor's Mayer hits tough floater over his defender) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Baylor's Mayer hits tough floater over his defender

videos.description: Jared Butler impresses with a nice catch-and-release triple to extend Baylor's big lead over Kansas State in the final minute of the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Butler drains long 3 to extend Baylor's big lead) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Butler drains long 3 to extend Baylor's big lead

videos.description: Baylor's Davion Mitchell doesn't let Kansas State get in his way as he puts a series of moves on the Wildcats' defense on his way to the hoop.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mitchell beats the shot clock carving through Kansas State's D) 2020/2/25

videos.headline: Mitchell beats the shot clock carving through Kansas State's D

videos.description: Flo Thamba puts the exclamation point on Baylor's blowout win vs. Kansas State with a monster slam.
